class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/9/b/0/2/thumb_40239682.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/9/1/2/4/thumb_279157156.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/e/8/5/thumb_283863717.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/5/f/1/thumb_272297905.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/4/4/8/thumb_252609288.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/c/5/2/thumb_247275442.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/9/b/a/thumb_245131162.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/c/c/thumb_283863276.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/e/9/a/a/thumb_257099818.jpeg\" /></div>          </div>          <p style=\"line-height:16px\">Do you want to set your website project up for success? Do you want to avoid any costly surprises along the way? Of course, you do. A thorough, focused web specification document will keep your web project running smoothly and, most importantly, will give you the best to chance of delivering a project that meets the goals of your visitors and your &#8230;</p>     </div>     <p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Glasgow-WordPress-Meetup/events/255764255/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"mu_button\"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p></div>\n</div></figure>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/2019/01/15/glasgow-meetup-1st-quarter-2019/feed/\";s:7:\